title: USGS, Chile earthquake shakemap at 0.3 second interval, Feb 27, 2010, Chile
name: USGS, Chile earthquake shakemap at 0.3 second interval, Feb 27, 2010, Chile
description: The poly shapefile is based on data released by USGS. It shows earth quake shakemap at 0.3 second interval. Look elsewhere on Finder for other shake maps such as vertical movement as well as time intervals shake maps for 0.3 second, 1 seconds and 3 seconds interval.
